error[[E0277]](https://doc.rust-lang.org/nightly/error_codes/E0277.html): the trait bound `Vec<bool>: Into<_>` is not satisfied
  --> src/main.rs:12:22
   |
12 |     let f: Foo = vec.into();
   |                      ^^^^ the trait `~const Into<_>` is not implemented for `Vec<bool>`
   |
   = note: required for `Vec<bool>` to implement `Into<Foo>`
help: consider borrowing here
   |
12 |     let f: Foo = (&vec).into();
   |                  ++   +
